><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p15" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ; line-height:22.5000pt; "><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">2、</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购网承诺遵循以下的原则运营网站，确保所有用户在</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购网中享受同等的权利与义务。</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p15" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ; line-height:22.5000pt; "><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">平等原则：用户和</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购在交易过程中具有同等的法律地位。</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p15" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ; line-height:22.5000pt; "><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">自由原则：用户享有自愿向</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购参与购买商品的权利，任何人不得非法干预。</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p15" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ; line-height:22.5000pt; "><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">公平原则：用户和</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购行使权利、履行义务应当遵循公平原则。</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p15" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ; line-height:22.5000pt; "><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">诚实信用原则：用户和</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购行使权利、履行义务应当遵循诚实信用原则。</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p15" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ; line-height:22.5000pt; "><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">履行义务原则：用户向</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购参与商品分享购买时，用户和</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购皆有有义务根据本服务协议的约定完成该等交易（法律或本协议禁止的交易除外）</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p15" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ; line-height:22.5000pt; "><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">3、用户知悉，除本协议另有约定外，用户无论是否获得商品，参与云购的资金均用于帮助他人，不能退回；用户完全了解参与</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购存在的风险，</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购网无法保证用户参与云购一定会获得商品。</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><h4 style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:22.5000pt; padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ; line-height:22.5000pt; "><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">四、用户的权利和义务</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;"><o:p></o:p></span></h4><p class="p15" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ; line-height:22.5000pt; "><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">1、用户有权拥有其在</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购的用户名及密码，并用该用户名和密码登录</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购参与商品购买。用户不得以任何形式转让或授权他人使用自己的</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购用户名。</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p15" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ; line-height:22.5000pt; "><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">2、用户有权根据本协议的规定以及</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购网站上发布的相关规则在</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购上查询商品信息、发表使用体验、参与商品讨论、邀请关注好友、上传商品图片、参加</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购的有关活动，以及享受</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购提供的其它信息服务</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p15" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ; line-height:22.5000pt; "><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">3、用户有义务在注册时提供自己的真实资料，并保证诸如电子邮件地址、联系电话、联系地址、邮政编码等内容的有效性及真实性，保证</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购可以通过上述联系方式与用户本人进行联系。同时，用户也有义务在相关资料发生变更时及时更新有关注册资料。用户保证不以他人资料在</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购进行注册和参与商品分享购买。</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p15" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ; line-height:22.5000pt; "><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">4、用户应当保证在</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购参与商品分享购买时遵守诚实信用原则，不扰乱网上交易的正常秩序。</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p15" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ; line-height:22.5000pt; "><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">5、用户在成为</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购的会员后，可按</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购的福分规则享受福分获得。累积福分可用于福分商城中的相应福分商品兑换。福分规则连同与该规则相关的条款和条件，构成用户与</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;">运</span><span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Tahoma;">购之间的完整协议。接受本协议，即表明接受